name: Portland ReactJS
tagline: A User Group for React in Portland, Oregon
body:
### We're just getting started

Please see our [Meetup Page](http://www.meetup.com/Portland-ReactJS). More to follow.
---
We are going to hang out next Tuesday, November 11th at 6pm for an informal meet/greet. If you can, please come and share your thoughts on this group and what you'd like to get from it and how you'd like to contribute. Meeting place TBD, but will be downtown/inner SE. Please [RSVP](http://www.meetup.com/Portland-ReactJS/events/217987022/) if you can so we have an idea of a head count. Look forward to meeting you all!
